OL,7,FThe numbers are most likely vague to
OL,8,Fprotect the identity of victims.
OL,10,FThe infected blood scandal has been
OL,11,Flabelled as the "worst treatment
OL,12,Fdisaster in the NHS", which saw more
OL,13,Fthan 30,000 people infected with HIV
OL,14,Fand Hepatitis C in the 1970s and 1980s.
OL,16,FDeputy Pursuant also asked what
OL,17,Fsupport victims received from Public
OL,18,FHealth and whether steps were taken to
OL,19,Fpursue compensation for islanders.
